{"id":"d9cb7a12-da37-495f-b925-7fc12627fdad","name":"Death Angel | ALIEN | A Quiet Place","description":"<p><strong>(Check out my other bots!)</strong></p><p><strong>ＬＭＡＯＯＯＯ. ｇｏｔ ｔｈｅ ｉｄｅａ ｆｒｏｍ ｔｈｅ ｍｏｖｉｅｓ. (Ｆｉｒｅ ｂｔｗ)</strong></p><p></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: #8bffee; color: inherit\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 244px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2299f818-b7dd-41a6-a872-abec2ddf9dd5_a5b8682f-f9d7-4562-8ed0-6262b8d431a7.webp?width=1000\"></mark></p><p>[𝗣𝗟𝗘𝗔𝗦𝗘] 𝗥𝗲𝗮𝗱 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗗𝗘𝗦𝗖 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝗮 𝗯𝗲𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗿 𝘂𝗻𝗱𝗲𝗿𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗻𝗱𝗶𝗻𝗴, (𝗜𝘁'𝘀 𝘀𝘂𝗽𝗽𝗼𝘀𝗲𝗱 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗥𝗣𝗚 𝗶𝗴???)</p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 245px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2299f818-b7dd-41a6-a872-abec2ddf9dd5_db04b289-d42c-4403-874e-0d90b5d0808e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>𝐖𝐚𝐫𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠: 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐛𝐨𝐭 𝐢𝐬 𝐦𝐲 𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐬𝐭, (𝐈𝐦 𝐭𝐫𝐲𝐢𝐧𝐠) 𝐬𝐨 𝐢𝐭'𝐬 𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐟𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐞𝐝, 𝐦𝐚𝐲 𝐛𝐞 𝐮𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐬𝐡𝐨𝐫𝐭.</p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 295px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2299f818-b7dd-41a6-a872-abec2ddf9dd5_6e2f15ff-2d3a-4412-90f2-9016c1cecf53.webp?width=1000\"><br><strong><em>𝕱𝖊𝖊𝖉𝖇𝖆𝖈𝖐 𝖎𝖘 𝖛𝖊𝖗𝖞 𝖒𝖚𝖈𝖍 𝖆𝖕𝖕𝖗𝖊𝖈𝖎𝖆𝖙𝖊𝖉, 𝖎𝖋 𝖎𝖙𝖘 𝖌𝖔𝖔𝖉 𝖔𝖗 𝖇𝖆𝖉, 𝖎𝖋 𝖎𝖙𝖘 𝖘𝖔𝖒𝖊𝖙𝖍𝖎𝖓𝖌 𝕴 𝖘𝖍𝖔𝖚𝖑𝖉 𝖋𝖎𝖝, 𝖆𝖉𝖉, 𝖔𝖗 𝖈𝖍𝖆𝖓𝖌𝖊, 𝕰𝖙𝖈.</em></strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"EG6m47J8ox0afgmhJ7CPo.webp","creator":"xX_Ser!sce_Xx","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🦹‍♂️ Villain","👹 Monster","⛓️ Dominant","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🔦 Horror"],"chats":1807,"messages":26609,"created_at":"2024-08-11T06:35:58.509708+00:00"}